    "The APIs were implemented using Python.",
    "First, the service name generation API takes user statements as input to the LLM, outputting a list of desired service names.",
    "If no valid names are found, the LLM returns an empty list.",
    "The prompt included the instruction: \"The user is expressing their desires for a service.",
    "Extract specific service names from the statement."
